    $V_{os}^0$ & Initial volume of solid components & $10 $ & $\mu m^3$ \\ \hline
    $V_{b}^0$ & Initial volume of solid components & $3 $ & $\mu m^3$\\ \hline
    $c_i^0$ & Initial inner osmolyte concentration & $322.2 $ & $mM$ \\ \hline
